deck: It's all out war between the Fantastic Four and the Inhumans!
description:
The Fantastic Four continue their onslaught against the Inhumans in the city of Attilan. As the battle rages on, the Seeker kidnaps Mr. Fantastic, Invisible Woman and the Thing while Human Torch falls back with the Inhumans, but they received a rather bitter greeting. Maximus the Mad has now declared himself the ruler of the Inhumans, and he demands to be wed to Medusa. Can the Fantastic Four stop him in time before it's too late?

Note: This episode is a direct adaptation and combination of Fantastic Four Issues #46 and #47.
name: Inhumans Saga Part 3: Beware the Hidden Land!
